<h1>Welcome to Ensim Analytics!</h1>
<p class="lead">Vous pouvez importer votre corpus ci dessous.<br>Si les données sont bien au format conformes ils seront importées et calculer.</p>
<p class="lead">Vous pouvez configurer les pondérations des reponses a chaques question dans la partie administration</p>
<div class="action-box">
    <%= link_to "Upload Corpus", new_data_import_path, class: "bg-white hover:bg-gray-100 text-gray-800 font-semibold py-2 px-4 border border-gray-400 rounded shado" %>
</div>
<br>
<h3 >Repartition des predictions selons les données deja importées</h3>

<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary">
  Nombres de Questions <span class="badge text-bg-secondary"><%=Question.count %></span>
</button>

<button type="button" class="btn btn-success">
  Nombres d"étudiants <span class="badge text-bg-primary"><%=Student.count - 1%></span>
</button>

<button type="button" class="btn btn-info">
  Prediction IPS <span class="badge text-bg-primary"><%=Student.where(predictedPath: "Ips").count%></span>
</button>

<button type="button" class="btn btn-info">
  Prediction Astre <span class="badge text-bg-primary"><%=Student.where(predictedPath: "Astre").count%></span>
</button>



<%= column_chart Student.group(:predictedPath).count %>